item.title: Help in make commands in server
item.dc:creator: @whattehp406 whattehp406
item.description:
@whattehp406 wrote:

[quote=“TOMSCAPE BETA, post:3, topic:368945”][quote author=whattehp406 link=topic=465078.msg3400947#msg3400947 date=1289926214]
i suggest starting at 317 and then moving on

L2C befor u go to higher revisions
everyone wants the high detail ones with nice stuff but they cant code and 508+ is 10X harder then 317
[/quote]

The only reason I found it more difficult starting a 508 + was the packaging, but he will get used to it as I did. All you need to work out is the new variables and folder layout.

@topic:

Use other peoples commands to learn off, then write your own:

http://tinyurl.com/27pprpe[/quote]i love let me google it for u
